{"type":"message","id":"cc03f765","parentId":"3c237380","timestamp":"2026-03-19T06:59:10.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context monitor shows that context usage is at 67%, which exceeds the 60% threshold. The script is alerting that a new session should be started to reset context. \n\nAccording to the skill description, when context usage exceeds 85%, it should automatically create a new session with loaded memory. Here it's at 67%, which is above the 60% threshold but below the 85% automatic threshold.\n\nLet me check what the HEARTBEAT.md says and whether there are any specific actions needed.","thinkingSignature":"b4e73e72b83447a1047236b96648627a8821c50515737e5ccb1680a72ffa3573"},{"type":"text","text":"Context usage is at **67%** (133,617/200,000 tokens), which exceeds the 60% threshold. It's not yet at the critical 85% threshold for automatic session creation, but getting close.\n\nLet me check if there's anything in HEARTBEAT.md that needs attention:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i5v0515e01am_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":355,"output":206,"cacheRead":37002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37563,"cost":{"input":0.0001065,"output":0.0002472,"cacheRead":0.00111006,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00146376}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773903530557}}
{"type":"message","id":"b18a5f57","parentId":"cc03f765","timestamp":"2026-03-19T06:59:10.545Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i5v0515e01am_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n\n## Context Manager Check\n\n- Run session_status to check current context usage\n- If context > 60%, consider saving memory and preparing for session switch\n- Check ~/proactivity/session-state.md for active tasks\n- Update ~/proactivity/memory/working-buffer.md if needed\n\n## Self-Improving Check\n\n- Read ./skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md\n- Use ~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md for last-run markers and action notes\n- If no file inside ~/self-improving/ changed since the last reviewed change, return HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n## Proactivity Check\n\n- Read ~/proactivity/heartbeat.md\n- Re-check active blockers, promised follow-ups, stale work, and missing decisions\n- Ask what useful check-in or next move would help right now\n- Message the user only when something changed or needs a decision\n- Update ~/proactivity/session-state.md after meaningful follow-through\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773903550543}}
